      • setSubscribedLibraryPlacement

        public SubscriptionsTypes.UpdateSpec.Builder setSubscribedLibraryPlacement(SubscriptionsTypes.UpdateSpecPlacement subscribedLibraryPlacement)
        Placement specification for the virtual machine template items of the subscribed library. Updating this information will only affect new or updated items, existing items will not be moved. The entire placement configuration of the subscribed library will replaced by the new specification. This property was added in vSphere API 6.7.2. If null, the placement configuration of the subscribed library will be unchanged.
        Parameters:
        subscribedLibraryPlacement - New value for the property.
